10. Of Affirmatiue neceſſarie Dueties, ſome are the weyghtier matters of the Lawe, [
                        〈 in non-Latin alphabet 〉
                     ] as Iudgement, Mercie, and Fayth, MATTH. 23.23. Others, leſſe weyghtie, ſuch as are thoſe of the Pearth Articles; which wee call neceſſarie, and yee doe reject.
